        p There are two types of trigger icons (icons placed next to dropdown labels) - plus/minus sign or arrows. To use first one simply put #[code.html span.trigger] into #[code.html label] tag and to use second one add to the #[code.html span] tag #[code.html .arrow] class. Direction of arrow is related to position of menu.

